{"tid":2387044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家依幾年有冇多咗注重私隱同安全？","createTime":"2021-01-30T04:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T07:16:43.000Z","uid":218158,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9041694b1039d7ff97872687f64e501077950986","tid":2387044,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:29:31.000Z","msg":"我諗當大家睇到依年幾嘅新聞都會越嚟越開始關注點樣保護自己嘅私隱同安全，但又唔知點樣做先好<br />\n<br />\n其實連登已經有唔少人出過教學，好多都做得好好，我就喺道一次過將啲我睇過認為有用嘅擺晒喺道，大家覺得有用就自己睇啦<br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明可以問我<br />\n<br />\n睇埋啲留言佢<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)     <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依個應該係大家最關注<br />\n【大整合+重開】電話+電腦+通訊+密碼+洗機消毒：保安+常見誤解           <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1956324/page/1?post=1239a57945a477bceec5cd00b9c9f9a6d78708a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1956324/page/1?post=1239a57945a477bceec5cd00b9c9f9a6d78708a1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有用，建議大家有時間全部睇一次<br />\n《資訊安全手冊》：香港全民網絡自我防衛指南          <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1235172/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1235172/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n較為基本<br />\n電腦手機私隱基本教學                  <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1294617/page/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1294617/page/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要喺晒啲留言道<br />\n大家平時會點改你個browser？      <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2338745/page/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2338745/page/</a>"},{"pid":"d44dbc23724b34fa4572bad599cc5887c7ba53dc","tid":2387044,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"大家睇完學識可以share埋畀週圍嘅人睇，甚至可以自己去教佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4784f34f9ce1e1cdc8d936c977b907226031d74","tid":2387044,"uid":281306,"like":1,"dislike":3,"sco